## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all aspects of the relationship between mental health and crime. The complexity of mental health issues and their interaction with various social and environmental factors means that conclusions drawn may not apply universally. Additionally, the data is limited to sources available up to October 2023, and newer studies may provide further insights.

